Chongqing is famous for its spicy hotpot and a great delicacy to see a flourishing new year. And the fiery dining experience is also becoming global. Over 20 years ago, spicy hotpot was almost unheard of. Nowadays, hotpot branches are expanding overseas. Brands such as Haidilao and Liuyishou are opening hundreds of restaurants around the world. CGTN Reporter Xu Xinchen joined with an iChongqing reporter to show you the fiery dining experience to see the new year.